  "title": "Outdoor Sales Executive (Up to $4500)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Outdoor Sales Executive (ID4101)<br />Location: Flexible location (Office at Woodlands)<br />Working Hour：<br />5 days work per week<br />Weekend (Saturday & Sunday) must work<br />2 weekdays off per week (off days can be requested)<br />Working hours: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM<br />Salary: $3000-$4500<br /><br />Outdoor Sales Executive<br /><br />Main Responsibilities<br />• Perform a professional, friendly and fun demonstration of a product.<br />• Prepared reports of business transactions and kept expense accounts.<br />• Motivated to close each and every sales opportunity while promoting the company image of professionalism, integrity, and quality.<br />• Process work order and complete all paperwork in accordance with approved and standardized procedures.<br />• Post-installation follow-up by contacting customer ensuring commitments were met and generating referrals.<br />• Skills Used Communication is the most effective way of getting sales.<br /><br />Requirements<br />• Candidates with Door to Door experience would be advantageous<br />• Able to start work immediately or within a short notice<br />• Welcome fresh graduates</p>",
